Sentencas: Effective sealant for planar solid oxide fuel cell is one technical hurdle for its application.
Titulo: Effective Ag-CuO sealant for planar solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this article, Ag-CuO braze, which conducted directly at 950 degrees C in air, has been investigated as a sealant candidate between the SS430 interconnect and the Ni/YSZ anode for the planar solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Effective Ag-CuO sealant for planar solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The results for leakage rates indicate that the lowest leakage is as low as 0.001 sccm cm(-1).
Titulo: Effective Ag-CuO sealant for planar solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: SEM images demonstrates that both the pure Ag and 6 mol% CuO in the braze integrates the anode inherently.
Titulo: Effective Ag-CuO sealant for planar solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: However pure Ag wets poorly on the SS430 interconnect surface but 6 mol% CuO braze forms a reaction zone, upon which Ag wets well, so the hermeticity has been improved significantly.
Titulo: Effective Ag-CuO sealant for planar solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Even after experiencing 20 thermal cycles, the leakage rate is still as low as 0.002 sccm cm(-1).
Titulo: Effective Ag-CuO sealant for planar solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: No significant effects of thermal cycles on the interfacial microstructure of the sealant were observed.
Titulo: Effective Ag-CuO sealant for planar solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: These shows that Ag-CuO braze is a promising candidate for SOFC sealant.
